68
00:04:56,663 --> 00:04:58,688
There you go.
Look, Molly.

69
00:04:59,599 --> 00:05:01,829
Tater tots.
Yourfaves.

70
00:05:01,868 --> 00:05:04,428
Mmm. Very good, very good.

