183
00:12:53,005 --> 00:12:54,734
Four years.

184
00:12:54,774 --> 00:12:56,708
What happened then?

185
00:12:57,710 --> 00:12:59,075
I graduated.

186
00:13:03,449 --> 00:13:05,917
I'm sorry.
I'm sorry, Mr. Singer.

187
00:13:05,951 --> 00:13:07,179
That's OK.

